<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Community Guidelines - <%= siteName %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Oxygen,
        Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Open Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      color: #1e293b;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--bg-white);
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: #0f172a;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: #334155;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 1rem 0 1rem 1.25rem;
      padding: 0;
      list-style-type: disc;
      color: #334155;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    a {
      color: #0ea5e9;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: #64748b;
      text-align: center;
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="container">
    <h1>Community Guidelines</h1>

  <p>Welcome to <%= siteName %>! We want to maintain a safe, respectful, and enjoyable community for everyone. These guidelines explain what we expect from our users and what you can expect from us.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>1. Be Respectful</h2>
  <p>Treat others with kindness and respect. Harassment, hate speech, threats, or discriminatory behavior based on race, ethnicity, gender, sexual orientation, religion, or disability will not be tolerated.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>2. No Spam or Self-Promotion</h2>
  <p>Please avoid posting spam, repetitive content, unsolicited advertisements, or excessive self-promotion.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>3. Share Appropriate Content</h2>
  <p>Only share content that is legal and appropriate for all audiences. Graphic, violent, or otherwise harmful content is prohibited.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>4. Protect Privacy</h2>
  <p>Do not share personal information about yourself or others, including addresses, phone numbers, or private communications.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>5. Follow Intellectual Property Laws</h2>
  <p>Only post content you own or have permission to share. Respect copyrights, trademarks, and other intellectual property rights.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>6. Report Violations</h2>
  <p>If you see content or behavior that violates these guidelines, please report it to us at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a>.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>7. Enforcement</h2>
  <p>We reserve the right to remove content and suspend or ban accounts that violate these guidelines or our Terms & Conditions.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>8. Changes to Guidelines</h2>
  <p>We may update these guidelines from time to time. Continued use of <%= siteName %> after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated guidelines.</p>

  <hr>

  
</main>
<footer>Last updated: August 10, 2025</footer>
</body>
</html>
